===Etymology===
Ultimately from the name of the [[w:Taurini|Taurini]] tribe. The name is probably from {{etyl|cel-pro|en}} {{m|cel-pro|*tur||water}} or {{m|cel-pro|*tauro||mountain}}. Connections to Latin {{m|la|taurus||bull}} are folk etymology.

